    <div begin="00:03.160" end="01:30.280">
      <p begin="00:03.160" end="00:05.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:03.160" end="00:03.470">Our</span> <span begin="00:03.470" end="00:03.620">sh</span><span begin="00:03.620" end="00:04.090">a</span><span begin="00:04.090" end="00:04.380">dow</span><span begin="00:04.380" end="00:04.490">s</span> <span begin="00:04.540" end="00:05.520">fall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">阴影悄然笼罩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">陰影悄然籠罩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">影が落ちゆく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리의 그림자가 드리워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nos ombres tombent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nuestras sombras caen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unsere Schatten fallen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nossas sombras caem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наши тени падают</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le nostre ombre cadono</span></p>
      <p begin="00:06.390" end="00:09.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:06.390" end="00:06.730">Where</span> <span begin="00:06.730" end="00:06.870">tr</span><span begin="00:06.870" end="00:07.180">u</span><span begin="00:07.180" end="00:07.280">th</span> <span begin="00:07.320" end="00:07.640">wa</span><span begin="00:07.640" end="00:07.720">s</span> <span begin="00:07.790" end="00:08.110">on</span><span begin="00:08.110" end="00:08.250">ce</span> <span begin="00:08.250" end="00:09.350">earn</span><span begin="00:09.350" end="00:09.380">ed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这曾探寻到真理的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這曾探尋到真理的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">かつて真実を掴み取った場所へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">한때 진실을 쟁취했던 그곳에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là où la vérité fut jadis acquise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Donde una vez se ganó la verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wo einst die Wahrheit errungen wurde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Onde a verdade um dia foi conquistada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Там где когда-то была обретена истина</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dove un tempo la verità fu conquistata</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10.560" end="00:12.890" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:10.560" end="00:10.950">We</span> <span begin="00:11.000" end="00:11.310">won't</span> <span begin="00:11.310" end="00:11.470">f</span><span begin="00:11.470" end="00:11.840">or</span><span begin="00:11.940" end="00:12.890">get</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们未曾忘却</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們未曾忘卻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">決して忘れない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리는 잊지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous n'oublierons pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No olvidaremos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir werden nicht vergessen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não esqueceremos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы не забудем</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non dimenticheremo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:13.760" end="00:16.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:13.760" end="00:14.250">The</span> <span begin="00:14.250" end="00:14.620">les</span><span begin="00:14.620" end="00:15.030">son</span><span begin="00:15.030" end="00:15.110">s</span> <span begin="00:15.170" end="00:15.470">we</span> <span begin="00:15.630" end="00:16.390">learn</span><span begin="00:16.390" end="00:16.420">ed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些铭刻于心的教诲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些銘刻於心的教誨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちが学んだ教訓を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리가 깨달은 그 교훈들을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les leçons que nous avons apprises</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las lecciones que aprendimos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Lehren die wir zogen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As lições que aprendemos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Уроки которые мы усвоили</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le lezioni che abbiamo imparato</span></p>
      <p begin="00:17.930" end="00:20.250" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:17.930" end="00:18.780">Pe</span><span begin="00:18.860" end="00:19.150">tal</span><span begin="00:19.150" end="00:19.240">s</span> <span begin="00:19.310" end="00:20.250">bloom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">繁花纵然盛放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">繁花縱然盛放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">花びらは咲き誇る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꽃잎은 피어나지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les pétales éclosent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los pétalos florecen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Blüten erblühen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pétalas desabrocham</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лепестки распускаются</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I petali sbocciano</span></p>
      <p begin="00:21.160" end="00:23.910" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:21.160" end="00:21.510">But</span> <span begin="00:21.620" end="00:22.040">they</span> <span begin="00:22.090" end="00:22.570">won</span><span begin="00:22.570" end="00:22.630">'t</span> <span begin="00:22.630" end="00:22.920">a</span><span begin="00:23.020" end="00:23.890">men</span><span begin="00:23.890" end="00:23.910">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">却无法修补残缺的过往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">卻無法修補殘缺的過往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">されど何も償えはしない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무것도 바로잡아 주진 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais ils ne répareront rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero no enmendarán</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Doch sie heilen nichts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas não vão remediar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но они ничего не исправят</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma non porranno rimedio</span></p>
